        "text": "=You are an expert ATS Resume Reviewer.\n\nYou will receive\n\nResume\n\nJob Description\n\nCompare both.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON.\n\n{\n\"overall_score\":0,\n\"ats_score\":0,\n\"job_match_score\":0,\n\"technical_score\":0,\n\"communication_score\":0,\n\"strengths\":[],\n\"weaknesses\":[],\n\"missing_skills\":[],\n\"matching_skills\":[],\n\"suggestions\":[],\n\"recommended_roles\":[],\n\"improved_summary\":\"\"\n}\n\nResume\n\n{{ $json.body.resume_text }}\n\nJob Description\n\n{{ $json.job_description }}",
